🍽️ Gourmet au Catering Website
This is a responsive catering website built using HTML and CSS. It showcases a catering service with sections like About, Menu, and Contact, providing a modern and clean layout.

📌 Features
Fixed Navigation Bar with hover effects

Hero Image Section with overlay text

About Section with text and image side by side

Menu Section listing food items and prices

Contact Section with address, contact info, and input form

Footer with credits

Responsive and clean design

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5 – Structure of the webpage

CSS3 – Styling and layout

Flexbox – For responsive layout alignment

📂 Project Structure
bash
Copy
Edit
├── index.html          # Main HTML file
├── catering.css        # External CSS file
├── hamburger.jpg       # Hero image
├── tablesetting2.jpg   # About section image
├── tablesetting.jpg    # Menu section image
└── README.md           # Project documentation
🚀 How to Use
Clone or download this repository.

Place all image files (hamburger.jpg, tablesetting2.jpg, tablesetting.jpg) in the same folder as index.html.

Open index.html in any modern browser.

